flowchart LR
A[Client: Donate Form] --> B[POST /api/razorpay-order]
B --> C[Backend creates Razorpay order in INR]
C --> D[Client opens Razorpay checkout]
D --> E[POST /api/razorpay-verify]
E --> F[Razorpay Webhook payment.captured/payment.failed]
F --> G[Verify webhook signature + persist event in Supabase]
G --> H[Idempotent donation status transition]
H --> I[Enqueue receipt_email job in Supabase]

I --> M[POST /api/jobs/receipt-email]
M --> N[Generate receipt PDF with PDFKit]
N --> O[Upload receipt to Supabase Storage]
O --> P[Download static NGO PDF from Supabase Storage]
P --> Q[Send email via Resend]
Q --> R[Mark receipt/email delivered]